Your Rights
Because all data stays on your device and we hold none of it, the rights to access, correct, delete, and port your data are always in your hands — directly on the device.
Data Retention
Since data is stored locally on your device, we do not have control over the retention of your data. Your data will remain on your device until you choose to delete it or uninstall the application.
Consent
By using our App, you consent to our Privacy Policy and agree to its terms.
